<div class=3D"text aem-GridColumn--phone--12 aem-GridColumn--phone--newline=
 aem-GridColumn aem-GridColumn--default--12 aem-GridColumn--offset--phone--=
0"><div id=3D"text-8f727aef70" class=3D"cmp-text ">
    <p>The Trip Cost Calculator below is designed to help agencies and driv=
ers select the most cost effective available option for state employee busi=
ness transportation as outlined in the <a href=3D"https://cms.illinois.gov/=
agency/vehicles/stateemployeebusinesstransportationpolicy.html">State Emplo=
yee Business Transportation Policy</a>. Drivers input the number of days an=
d miles for upcoming travel. The calculator displays the associated cost an=
d from there you can choose the form of transportation which is most econom=
ical.<br>
</p>

</div>

   =20

</div>
